text: "Here We Are" is a 1991 song by American country band Alabama and is the fifth and final single from their 13th studio album Pass It On Down. It went to number 3 on the Canadian RPM Country Tracks and number 2 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart. It was written by Vince Gill. ==References== Category:1991 songs Category:Country songs Category:Alabama (band) songs
